---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Cinta Kafe | Kopi Terbaik dengan Sepenuh Hati"
  description="Nikmati suasana tenang dan kopi pilihan berkualitas tinggi di Cinta Kafe. Tempat berkumpul yang modern, profesional, dan elegan."
>
  <nav class="flex justify-between items-center px-8 py-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-2xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-bold tracking-tight">
      CINTA KAFE.
    </div>
    <div
      class="hidden md:flex gap-8 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-widest"
    >
      <a href="#about" class="hover:text-amber-700 transition">Tentang Kami</a>
      <a href="#menu" class="hover:text-amber-700 transition">Menu</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-amber-700 transition">Kontak</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section
      class="relative h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center text-center px-4"
    >
      <div class="z-10">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-['Playfair_Display'] mb-6">
          Secangkir Kopi,<br />Sejuta Cerita.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Menghadirkan biji kopi pilihan dari petani lokal untuk menciptakan
          momen tak terlupakan di setiap tegukan.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#menu"
          class="bg-stone-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-amber-800 transition"
          >Lihat Menu Kami</a
        >
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="menu" class="bg-stone-100 py-20 px-8">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-['Playfair_Display'] mb-12 text-center">
          Menu Spesialis Kami
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="h-80 bg-stone-300 mb-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
              <div
                class="w-full h-full bg-stone-400 group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Signature Latte</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-500">
              Espresso lembut dengan susu oat organik.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <div class="h-80 bg-stone-300 mb-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
              <div
                class="w-full h-full bg-stone-400 group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Manual Brew</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-500">
              Biji single-origin pilihan dengan teknik V60.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <div class="h-80 bg-stone-300 mb-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
              <div
                class="w-full h-full bg-stone-400 group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Cold Brew Honey</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-500">
              Kopi dingin fermentasi 12 jam dengan madu hutan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer id="contact" class="bg-stone-900 text-stone-400 py-16 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-['Playfair_Display'] mb-6">
          Cinta Kafe.
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Jl. Melati No. 123, Jakarta Selatan</p>
        <p>Senin - Minggu | 08:00 - 22:00</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:items-end">
        <p class="text-white mb-4">Ikuti Perjalanan Kami</p>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Instagram</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">TikTok</a>
          <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
